#. [ending_screen / labels] key: made_for_gwj
msgid "Made for Godot Wild Jam #63"
msgstr "为 Godot Wild Jam #63 制作"

#. [ending_screen / subtitles] key: subtitle_5
msgid "My contact's gone dark."
msgstr "我的线人彻底失联了。"

#. [ending_screen / subtitles] key: subtitle_7
msgid "Hope they're enjoying the fallout."
msgstr "希望他们正好好享受这场烂摊子。"

#. [ending_screen / subtitles] key: subtitle_8
msgid "As for me: I'll lie low for a while."
msgstr "至于我嘛，得先躲一阵子避避风头。"

#. [ending_screen / subtitles] key: subtitle_1
msgid "See, here's the thing about making powerful people angry..."
msgstr "你知道的，惹了大人物，下场一般都不怎么好看……"

#. [ending_screen / subtitles] key: subtitle_6
msgid "For all I know, they were in on the plan all along."
msgstr "据我所知，他们从一开始就跟这事脱不了干系。"

#. [ending_screen / subtitles] key: subtitle_4
msgid "It's a miracle I made it out of there with my tail still on."
msgstr "我能毫发无伤地逃出来，真是个奇迹！"

#. [ending_screen / subtitles] key: subtitle_2
msgid "You've gotta do it from a distance."
msgstr "这种事就得躲得远远的干。"

#. [ending_screen / subtitles] key: subtitle_9
msgid "It's far from home... but there are worse places to be when you're in hiding."
msgstr "这地方离家是远了点…… 但要藏身，这儿已经算不错了。"

#. [ending_screen / subtitles] key: subtitle_3
msgid "That, or make sure you're already running in the opposite direction by the time they find out."
msgstr "要么就趁早跑路，等他们反应过来，你早就跑没影了。"

